'''Captain Brackenbrook''' is the leader of [[Archet]]'s garrison.<ref name="Captain">[[The Lord of the Rings Online]], Introduction, ''Intro: Captain Brackenbrook''</ref> Captain Brackenbrook is mostly found in the Mad Badger Inn, from where he commands the garrison.<ref name="Captain"/> He was killed in the Assault of Archet.<ref>[[The Lord of the Rings Online]], Introduction, ''Instance: The Assault on Archet''</ref> After his death his son, [[Jon Brackenbrook|Jon]], succeeds him as captain.<ref>[[The Lord of the Rings Online]], Introduction, ''Intro: The Assault on Archet''</ref>
